  "3039260": {
    "name": "Lumo 2",
    "steam_appid": 3039260,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039260/extras/73a0a2972d5a49feb76e4782d64942f1.avif?t=1760779114\" width=616 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Lumo 2》中，你将踏入一个充满天马行空想象力的奇妙世界。每个房间都是新挑战，每场挑战都有新花样。从跳跃冲刺突破障碍到开动脑筋破解谜题，你将在不断变化的操作视角与机制中开辟新道路、解锁新能力。无论是追求全收集完美通关，还是悠闲探图走走看看，下个角落总有惊喜在等你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039260/extras/97156cb3153b3034bb737446e72b85c9.poster.avif?t=1760779114\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039260/extras/97156cb3153b3034bb737446e72b85c9.webm?t=1760779114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039260/extras/97156cb3153b3034bb737446e72b85c9.mp4?t=1760779114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中的关卡有各自独特的规则与挑战，运用你的反应力和观察力在充满变化的关卡中走开辟出属于自己的道路吧。也许上一刻你还在3D迷宫中闪避陷阱，下一刻就已转入俯视角解谜，或是奔跑在街机风格的小游戏里……每个区域都截然不同，每个新空间都值得探索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里完全适合各种游玩风格。无论是身经百战的老玩家，还是毫无经验的萌新，都能找到最适合自己的冒险节奏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039260/extras/822c0d311723627faa575ae4d1ee7cb4.poster.avif?t=1760779114\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039260/extras/822c0d311723627faa575ae4d1ee7cb4.webm?t=1760779114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039260/extras/822c0d311723627faa575ae4d1ee7cb4.mp4?t=1760779114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Lumo 2》在初代内容的基础上，新加入了三个精心设计的新场景可供探索。你需要时刻保持警惕：躲开陷阱、跳上平台，同时开动脑筋破解谜题，穿梭在相互连通的房间之间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从穿越尖刺机关到踩格子大作战，每一项挑战都独具特色。别忘记在闪转腾挪之余保持思考。毕竟，聪明的头脑正是在这个世界中前进的最大助力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039260/extras/b35d1661b2a71ca0cac5e6f5d2a590e8.poster.avif?t=1760779114\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039260/extras/b35d1661b2a71ca0cac5e6f5d2a590e8.webm?t=1760779114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039260/extras/b35d1661b2a71ca0cac5e6f5d2a590e8.mp4?t=1760779114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >好奇心会带你找到一切。《Lumo 2》中处处暗藏惊喜，复古磁带、橡皮鸭子，还有那些致敬经典游戏的彩蛋，这里的每个角落都值得一探。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当然，你无需收集一切也能完成故事。究竟是找到所有隐藏物品达成全收集？还是在探索中享受每个意外之喜？由你决定</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039260/extras/8ca8ae12efe9e9bd19b9c86674cd0c83.poster.avif?t=1760779114\" width=1170 height=670 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039260/extras/8ca8ae12efe9e9bd19b9c86674cd0c83.webm?t=1760779114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039260/extras/8ca8ae12efe9e9bd19b9c86674cd0c83.mp4?t=1760779114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >戴上帽子，点亮法杖，跃入这满是奇思妙想的缤纷世界吧！无论你为何而来，这里总有新发现等着你。马上将《Lumo 2》加入愿望单，准备踏上探索之旅吧！<br> </p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 芬兰语, 日语, 韩语, 简体中文, 繁体中文, 威尔士语",
